th-Richards-and-Lou-Reed-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Keith-Richards-and-Lou-Reed-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Keith-Richards-and-Lou-Reed-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Keith-Richards-and-Lou-Reed-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Keith-Richards-and-Lou-Reed-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/keith-richards">基思·理查兹 (Keith Richards)</a>在发行新的致敬专辑以纪念这位纽约偶像之前，翻唱了<a href="/artists/lou-reed">卢·里德 (Lou Reed)</a>的《I&#39;m Waiting For The Man》。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><b>阅读更多：</b> <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/classic-albums-turn-50-2023-1973-3370169"><b>这些 1973 年的经典专辑将于 2023 年迎来 50 岁生日</b></a></li></ul><p>理查兹翻唱的《I&#39;m Waiting For The Man》是在 Reed 3 月 2 日生日前一天翻唱的。这首歌是 Reed 最早的作品之一，出现在地下丝绒乐队 1967 年的首张专辑《The Velvet Underground &amp; Nico》中。</p><p>在一份声明中（根据<em><a href="https://consequence.net/2024/03/lou-reed-tribute-album-keith-richards-cover/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">《声音的后果</a></em>》）谈到这位前丝绒地下乐队主唱时，理查兹说：“对我来说，卢很突出。真正的交易！ [他]对美国音乐和所有音乐都很重要！我想念他和他的狗。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Keith Richards - 我在等待那个男人（Lou Reed 封面）（官方视频）" width="696" height="522" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/5NcJvi5TYEk?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> 《I&#39;m Waiting On A Man》的翻唱是即将发行的 Lou Reed 致敬专辑《The Power of the Heart》中的第一首歌曲。该密纹唱片还收录了<a href="/artists/angel-olsen">Angel Olsen</a> 、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-afghan-whigs">阿富汗辉格党</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/joan-jett">Joan Jett</a>和 Blackhearts、Rosanne Cash 和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lucinda-williams">Lucinda Williams</a>等人的贡献。</p><p> 《The Power Of The Heart》将于 4 月 20 日通过 Light in the Attic 发行（<a href="https://link.lightintheattic.net/im-waiting-for-the-man" target="_blank" rel="noopener">预先保存在此处</a>）。它将在今年的唱片店日以限量版黑胶唱片形式以及 CD 和所有流媒体平台上发售。所有实体格式都将包括米克·洛克和蒂莫西·格林菲尔德-桑德斯拍摄的里德照片，以及专辑制作人、里德的亲密合作者比尔·本特利撰写的内页注释。</p><p>这张专辑是与里德的遗孀劳里·安德森和卢·里德档案馆合作制作的。该档案系列于 2022 年推出，发行了获得格莱美提名的专辑“Words &amp; Music, May 1965”。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C3-WiOurMEl/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M54